== Overview ==
The Targeting Subroutine enhances a bots offensive ability by increasing accuracy and the chance to inflict critical hits.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Targeting Subroutine can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in [[Vulcore]].
